<i>noun</i>: 알뜰 [알뜰], 검약 [거ː먁] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>알뜰 [알뜰]</dt><br>
<dd>frugality; thrift</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 살림을 규모 있고 계획성 있게 하여 빈틈이 없음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of keeping the economy of one's household thoroughly and as planned.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>검약 [거ː먁]</dt><br>
<dd>economy; thrift; frugality</dd><br>
<dd>돈이나 물건 등을 아껴 씀.</dd><br>
<dd>Using money or objects sparingly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>